No. 616. The United States, Petitioner, v. Ninety-nine Diamonds. April 2, 1906. The Attorney General, The Solicitor Gen-eral and Mr. Assistant Attorney General McReynolds for petitioner. Mr. W. Wickham Smith and Mr. John K. Maxwell for' respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
